      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "f0def03ebd62fd2f",
      "text": "We would like to distribute node and relation definitions throughout the scripts. We anticipate a need for finding these so will build this tool first. [https://github.com/WardCunningham/search/commit/f595d918c1d1390fc65ad6fc9466e2887103733f github]"
